<br>
When you first come in, you will see 2 mobs. One on either side of a wall. More than likely, you will have to fight both at the same time (off tank).  Get a tank and cleric on one, and everyone else on the other.  Get one dead, so even if you wind up wiping out (a decent possiblity) getting in there again and completing the breakin will not be impossible.<br>
<br>
